						<div id="ctl00_PlaceHolderMiddle_MiddleContent__ControlWrapper_RichHtmlField" style="display:inline"><p><font size=2 face=Arial></font> </p>
<p><font size=2 face=Arial>HTB provides customized fine art / collections insurance programs for museums, cultural institutions, exhibitions, universities and colleges, commercial galleries and private dealers, personal and corporate collections, artists, conservators and framers, auction houses and antiques dealers, and art consultants. </font></p>
<p><font size=2 face=Arial>Working closely with you, our specialists can design an insurance package that responds to the specific coverage needs of your collection.
